# > 京小超
京小超 = type=cron,cronexp=11 1-23/2 * * *,wake-system=1,timeout=300,script-path=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lxk0301/jd_scripts/master/jd_superMarket.js,script-update-interval=0

# > 京小超兑换奖品
